latestPosts.caption:
Cozy Calm Night routine—aka my favorite part of the day where I pretend I have my life together lol 😂😌. It starts with me tying my hair like I’m about to fight a boss battle (spoiler: it’s just my skincare), followed by twenty minutes of staring into the mirror like I’m about to get cast in a K-drama. Cleanser, toner, serum, moisturizer—each step performed with the grace of a sleepy sloth. I threw in a lil’ haircare too, because why not? My hair deserves love for surviving whatever this day was. 😅 

Honestly, this routine is equal parts self-care and me stalling bedtime, but it works. I go to sleep looking like a glazed donut and wake up… still tired, but at least my skin’s glowing! ✨💤

I started using this beautiful body scrub from @loccitaneindia . I have a very dry and bad skin condition due to that i can’t use any type of scrub but this one is chef’s kiss 💋. So smooth and hydrating absolutely in love. 

Started using retinol recently and loving @wishtrend vitamin A Bakuchiol night cream. So lightweight and such a beginner friendly anti aging cream. Makes skin glowing and also reduced some pigmentation mark. 

As always i am a huge fan of @theordinary peptide hair serum, it’s the only hair treatment that i use. It’s a little sticky in formula but i think i have felt a difference in my hair growth journey. 

Lastly my favourite moisturiser @esteelauderin revitalising supreme + night repair. It’s extremely lightweight and very hydrating. 
.
.
Let me know if you have any questions ♥️ and comment below for the link 🔗 

.
.

Hi i am Antara and i just hit 100k followers. This is just a number but it’s not just a number, we can count numbers but we can’t really explain our feelings. We can count numbers like 1,00,000 of you who are here to support what i do, but i am here to say how i feel about this number to 1,00,000 of you. Truly when i started my journey it was just to create some connection with some of you, just to create something which i genuinely love.I always loved makeup! my passion for makeup is something different, It’s pure joy of testing different formulas. Years after years i have seen so much changes in the beauty community and it brought me so much knowledge. I still buy 100 makeup products randomly just to test out the formulas because i have to recommend it to you all. I am so deeply connected with you guys that just cannot randomly suggest you a product, i have to know that you loved my recommendation. We measure our success journey with numbers here on instagram but this number is to make more progress in my work. This number is to let myself know that if 1,00,000 people can love what i do ( tears dripping from my eyes) then i will surely never stop doing this. I will keep on working hard and be proud of the efforts i’ve put. 
Thank you so much for being there with me as always. 🌷✨
.
.
.
.
